<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/crossrail-international> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Crossrail International (CI) was established by the Department for Transport to help promote UK businesses abroad. It is a specialist advisory practice that works with UK partners to provide strategic advice to clients on the development and delivery of complex rail and metro schemes across the globe. CI is a public corporation of the Department for Transport ."@en .
